
All
              History majors must register for Hist 201 (Intro to
              Historiography) in the Fall of their Sophomore year.
If
              you have a student interested in History, please
              refer them to Dr. Tim Whisler, Scotus 315, ext. 3312 or Dr.
              Deirdre Moloney, Scotus 316A, ext. 3310.

The
              History Department does not advise their own first-year students.
